        Coord getCoord()
        Returns:
        the coordinate of the activity, possibly null.

        Note that there is deliberately no way to set the coordinate except at creation. We might consider something like moveActivityTo( linkid, coord ). kai, aug'10

      • getLinkId

        Id<Link> getLinkId()
        Returns:
        the if of the link to which the activity is attached. This may start as null, but is usually set automatically by the control(l)er before the zeroth iteration.

        Note that there is deliberately no way to set the link id except at creation. We might consider something like moveActivityTo( linkid, coord ). kai, aug'10
